name: Think About It (ft. Jburn)
description:
Bases | Think About It (ft. Jburn) | Music and Animation

-----

Think About was written in November of 2020, during the height of the pandemic. The artwork, mix and master have been developed over the course of one year and the project is now available exclusively here. 

Contemplative, enthralling and hopeful.


Music by Darryl Kirchner and JBurn
Artwork and Animation by Darryl Kirchner
